#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn12.42"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.42:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.42:0.2"
msgid "5. Gahapativagga "
msgstr "5. Householders "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 42. Dutiyapañcaverabhayasutta → dutiyapañcabhayaverasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn12.42:0.3"
msgid "42. Dutiyapañcaverabhayasutta "
msgstr "42. Dangers and Threats (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.71, sc1
msgctxt "sn12.42:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.42:1.2"
msgid "“Yato kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti, catūhi ca sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti, ariyo cassa ñāyo paññāya sudiṭṭho hoti suppaṭividdho, so ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when a noble disciple has quelled five dangers and threats, has the four factors of stream-entry, and has clearly seen and comprehended the noble cycle with wisdom, they may, if they wish, declare of themselves: "

msgctxt "sn12.42:1.3"
msgid "‘khīṇanirayomhi … pe … avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyano’ti. "
msgstr "‘I’ve finished with rebirth in hell, the animal realm, and the ghost realm. I’ve finished with all places of loss, bad places, the underworld. I am a stream-enterer! I’m not liable to be reborn in the underworld, and am bound for awakening.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn12.42:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti? "
msgstr "What are the five dangers and threats they have quelled? "

msgctxt "sn12.42:2.2"
msgid "Yaṃ, bhikkhave, pāṇātipātī … pe … "
msgstr "Killing living creatures … "

msgctxt "sn12.42:2.3"
msgid "yaṃ, bhikkhave, adinnādāyī … "
msgstr "stealing … "

msgctxt "sn12.42:2.4"
msgid "yaṃ, bhikkhave, kāmesumicchācārī … "
msgstr "sexual misconduct … "

msgctxt "sn12.42:2.5"
msgid "yaṃ, bhikkhave, musāvādī … "
msgstr "lying … "

msgctxt "sn12.42:2.6"
msgid "yaṃ, bhikkhave, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyī … pe … "
msgstr "taking alcoholic drinks that cause negligence … "

msgctxt "sn12.42:2.7"
msgid "imāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti. "
msgstr "These are the five dangers and threats they have quelled. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn12.42:3.1"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti? "
msgstr "What are the four factors of stream-entry that they have? "

msgctxt "sn12.42:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe … pe … "
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn12.42:3.3"
msgid "dhamme … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn12.42:3.4"
msgid "saṅghe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn12.42:3.5"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti. "
msgstr "and their ethical conduct is loved by the noble ones. "

msgctxt "sn12.42:3.6"
msgid "Imehi catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti. "
msgstr "These are the four factors of stream-entry that they have. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn12.42:4.1"
msgid "Katamo cassa ariyo ñāyo paññāya sudiṭṭho hoti suppaṭividdho? "
msgstr "And what is the noble cycle that they have clearly seen and comprehended with wisdom? "

msgctxt "sn12.42:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako paṭiccasamuppādaññeva sādhukaṃ yoniso manasi karoti … pe … "
msgstr "A noble disciple carefully and properly attends to dependent origination itself … "

msgctxt "sn12.42:4.3"
msgid "ayamassa ariyo ñāyo paññāya sudiṭṭho hoti suppaṭividdho. "
msgstr "This is the noble cycle that they have clearly seen and comprehended with wisdom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn12.42:5.1"
msgid "Yato kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa imāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti, imehi catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti, ayañcassa ariyo ñāyo paññāya sudiṭṭho hoti suppaṭividdho, so ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya: "
msgstr "When a noble disciple has quelled five dangers and threats, has the four factors of stream-entry, and has clearly seen and comprehended the noble cycle with wisdom, they may, if they wish, declare of themselves: "

msgctxt "sn12.42:5.2"
msgid "‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto, sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyano’”ti. "
msgstr "‘I’ve finished with rebirth in hell, the animal realm, and the ghost realm. I’ve finished with all places of loss, bad places, the underworld. I am a stream-enterer! I’m not liable to be reborn in the underworld, and am bound for awakening.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.42:5.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

